{"tid":2218033,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Ellen DeGeneres疑陷財困 放售價值近8千萬藝術品","createTime":"2020-09-26T02:22:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T05:02:43.000Z","uid":130626,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d62dc438177a0a1df2efcb0a5704d0f6399e30a2","tid":2218033,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T02:22:01.000Z","msg":"美國同志名嘴艾倫迪格納絲（Ellen DeGeneres）節目《The Ellen DeGeneres Show》早前被員工控訴，除了大爆艾倫在私底下為人粗魯無禮，又指節目工作環境不良，存在種族歧視、欺凌、恐嚇甚至性騷擾。雖然最近她正式於節目中道歉，但仍未能挽救事業，更要將家中價值美金1千萬（約港幣7,800萬）藝術品賣出救亡，似乎已陷入財困。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200926/RQIGUYMVE5DTXBBR47CRAHQSD4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200926%2FRQIGUYMVE5DTXBBR47CRAHQSD4%2F&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu6GvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=4c914237\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200926%2FRQIGUYMVE5DTXBBR47CRAHQSD4%2F&h=c26e65db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200926/RQIGUYMVE5DTXBBR47CRAHQSD4/</a>"},{"pid":"5747edc2fa4cfe54880dc678c9562de1d6d9b7cd","tid":2218033,"uid":27324,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T02:42:00.000Z","msg":"呢條垃圾 竟然仲未比人換走"},{"pid":"ea4e771727b1fd8e4c659697ed8331c209ce0247","tid":2218033,"uid":33077,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T02:42:54.000Z","msg":"係就真係抵佢"},{"pid":"79d18b667ce4ef7ffda64fa3d915f789fb32b84e","tid":2218033,"uid":136416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T02:43:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98131b109853a29df2865b257b27b65fc0c20fb9","tid":2218033,"uid":107881,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T02:44:42.000Z","msg":"點解會即刻財困"},{"pid":"47aafa88fe68caacb3f563886d3e84588fd4e845","tid":2218033,"uid":27324,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"98131b109